Rehn Says EU Needs to Contain Turbulence in Financial Markets

-- B y   A n d r e w   C l a p h a m
-- 
2011-09-15T09:46:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/rehn-says-eu-needs-to-contain-turbulence-in-financial-markets.html
The Europena Union needs to contain
the turbulence in financial markets, EU Economic and Monetary
Commissioner  Olli Rehn  told reporters in Brussels today.  “We have to contain the turbulence in the financial
markets and we have to restore confidence in the economy and our
ability to manage the sovereign debt crisis,” Rehn said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
